**Income tax surcharge** applies when your taxable income exceeds ₹50 lakh: 10% surcharge on ₹50L–₹1Cr, 15% on ₹1Cr–₹2Cr, 25% on ₹2Cr–₹5Cr, and 25% above ₹5Cr (reduced from 37% under new regime). Health & Education Cess of 4% applies on (tax + surcharge). This calculator computes the exact total tax liability.
